title: The Thug I Chose 3 by Tina J.epub
description:
In the final installment of The Thug I Chose, relationships are still being tested.

Polo is trying to bring everyone down in order to get back to Heaven. Asia revealed a secret that was unknown to everyone; yet causes turmoil once again between Day and Heaven.
Mariah comes face to face with Mitch's past, but not without dangerous consequences. Angela has to deal with someone reentering her life and trying to take what is now hers.
Heaven figures out a way to take Polo down; to rid him out of their life forever, but will Dayquan go along with the plan and allow her to put herself in harms way.
Will any of them succeed in getting what they really want?
